title: 12. Answering Your DMs + Top Esthetics Qs!
description:
Hi! In part i of our Q+A series we are answering your big questions about esthetics-- from our top tips  for success to our horror stories! We would love to hear what you think - leave us a comment on Instagram and leave us a review! Looking forward to your feedback! Xo, Tess + Lo
